+# BUILD_PR - PR_26124_070-palette-manager-css-dead-override-cleanup
+
+## Purpose
+Perform one scoped Palette Manager V2 CSS cleanup by removing only confirmed dead or duplicate override blocks from `paletteManagerV2.css`.
+
